flowchart LR

  TF["🛠️ Terraform<br/>Provisions infra + alert rules (Alert-as-Code)"]
  SM["🔑 Secrets Manager<br/>Stores Grafana Cloud credentials"]
  Slack["💬 Slack<br/>Receives alert notifications"]

  subgraph Cluster["☸️ EKS Cluster"]
    ESO["🔐 External Secrets<br/>Injects secrets into cluster"]
    Dagster["⚙️ Dagster Workloads<br/>Generate application logs"]
    Events["📣 Kubernetes Events<br/>Cluster/runtime events"]
    Alloy["📡 Grafana Alloy<br/>Collects, enriches, and forwards logs"]
  end

  subgraph GrafanaCloud["☁️ Grafana Cloud"]
    Loki["🪵 Loki<br/>Centralized log backend"]
    Explore["📊 Dashboards / Explore<br/>Search and investigate logs"]
    Rules["🚨 Alerting Rules<br/>Defined via Terraform (Alert-as-Code)"]
  end

  %% Secret flow
  SM --> ESO
  ESO --> Alloy

  %% Log flow
  Dagster --> Alloy
  Events --> Alloy
  Alloy --> Loki

  %% Observability flow
  Loki --> Explore
  Loki --> Rules

  %% Alerting flow
  Rules --> Slack

  %% Alert-as-code connection
  TF --> Rules